<p>流行朋克老将<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sum-41">Sum 41</a>将与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jessie-ware">Jessie Ware</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/tom-morello">Tom Morello</a>一起成为倒数第二天的主角，后者因担任<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/rage-against-the-machine">Rage Against The Machine</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/audioslave">Audioslave</a>乐队的吉他手而闻名。</p><p>最后，2024 年版《Mad Cool》的最后一晚<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bring-me-the-horizon">，《Bring Me The Horizo​​n》</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/avril-lavigne">艾薇儿·拉维尼</a>将成为头条新闻， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/arlo-parks">Arlo Parks</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ashnikko">Ashnikko</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-gaslight-anthem">The Gaslight Anthem</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/genesis-owusu">Genesis Owusu</a>也会继续表演。预计很快就会公布更多艺术家，您可以在下面的海报中查看当前的阵容。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C0tkX1ZNQZR/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" ve